# Summary
This documentation details the Userflow integration with Amplitude, enabling teams to stream user onboarding events (like flow starts and checklist completions) to Amplitude for behavioral analytics, while also allowing Amplitude cohorts to be used for creating personalized in-app experiences in Userflow without requiring developer resources.

